Package com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog

Class DailyBasalHistoryLog

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog.HistoryLog
      • com.jwoglom.pumpx2.pump.messages.response.historyLog.DailyBasalHistoryLog
  • public class DailyBasalHistoryLog
extends HistoryLog
    A message which appears in the history log every hour at minimum, more frequently when the basal rate changes, and contains a summary of the total basal deliveries up to that point in the current day. Resets at 00:00 midnight when there is a NewDayHistoryLog.
